            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Fortissimo</supplied><supplied reason="lost">Fortissimo</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">nobilissi</supplied>mo Caesari <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Flavio V</supplied>alerio Constan<lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">tio</supplied> Lepcitani <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">de</supplied>voti numini maies<lb break="no" n="6"/>tatique eius publice
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: zwischen 1. März 293 und 1. Mai 305. The inscription is carved over an erased earlier one.</p>
            </div>
